{"tid":1807872,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"雲海: 區議員立即向自己當區醫院查詢有冇疑似案例作出紀錄！","createTime":"2020-01-02T04:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T12:18:39.000Z","uid":7971,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"91cd8476f983cd06d4bbaae0c7d6f63b1c5987f9","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"其實我係唔想教㗎！係原本區議員當選就係要做嘢唔係要學嘢！但今日例外啦！若果你係新當選嘅區議員，就近日嘅疑似武漢沙士入侵香港事件，￼你哋而家已經可以好撚多嘢可以做￼￼￼￼￼￼、包括：<br />\n1向自己當區醫院￼查詢有冇疑似案例作出紀錄￼￼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2向衛生署書面及口頭質詢有冇任何個案、疑似個案、以及應變方法等等！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n￼￼￼3.向醫管局書面及口頭質詢有冇任何個案、疑似個案以及應變方法等等￼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.向自己當區各私家醫生詢問有冇疑似個案作紀錄￼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.向政府部門查詢有冇大陸病情互相通報記錄等等！￼冇就屌佢違反協議！有就屌佢點解唔公布！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n￼￼<br />\n以前我真係會傻到自己做㗎，￼炸兩俠做唔到咁多野㗎啦￼！各位區議員素人醒啦喂！￼上任第二日啦大佬！￼啲政府部門電話號碼唔使問我攞掛？你未ready晒喺手唔該退出區議會￼￼！<br />\nPs仲有，向機場管理局質詢，最新檢疫行動點樣安排同埋轉介左幾多個案比衛生署！<br />\n<br />\nSource: 雲海Facebook"},{"pid":"74945e48c03d1184193ab96b4bee60f71310860b","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">1向自己當區醫院￼查詢有冇疑似案例作出紀錄￼￼！<br />\n2向衛生署書面及口頭質詢有冇任何個案、疑似個案、以及應變方法等等！<br />\n￼￼￼3.向醫管局書面及口頭質詢有冇任何個案、疑似個案以及應變方法等等￼！<br />\n4.向自己當區各私家醫生詢問有冇疑似個案作紀錄￼！<br />\n5.向政府部門查詢有冇大陸病情互相通報記錄等等！￼冇就屌佢違反協議！有就屌佢點解唔公布！</span>"},{"pid":"122e75565a397c11db7178398acb3b98c5694741","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"做野啦 新當選個班 機會黎<br />\n寫個email 打個電話就得"},{"pid":"ab91deaf6bcaefd4a41b539cf51394cc24ae73c9","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b41654649724a08ff8ce905b8f5c2d34f38fdfe3","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:40:25.000Z","msg":"唔該做做野"},{"pid":"4ecff2e2f8b53550d3e97746520925916b49e72f","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"你哋個啲地區咩咩網絡，咩咩起步<br />\n<br />\n分team人<br />\n一team email俾衛生署，HA<br />\n再去哂衛生署自己地區個診所，同地區醫院<br />\n<br />\n另一team人 就去私家診所問下<br />\n<br />\n機會就係你面前<br />\n做野好嘛"},{"pid":"029c57474f830c9dee0341b7998e0e37f8232b4b","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:42:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b60a2151b68f465f33c5987e3951fbcedd18813c","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:43:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"95fe939c5cd03c354c3eedfc201a018aa7396a97","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:43:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"80a762a52e5233c66c1de867246dc29659cc3b1a","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0000a228bebf2b7b7e4a5ed5e93af3c951adea8e","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9d65ecdf15a0fde04b4303469f7117ea6c191334","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:46:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9dce9844f88b7d05d4ee0e6694c9e47b763a8d67","tid":1807872,"uid":124859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:47:54.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"b5c2a787f6a04fea746074a20a5ad0cdcae3fc05","tid":1807872,"uid":139578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:49:14.000Z","msg":"咁撚大獲 推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae0eee5a415ec2ab970ea605f6441b69684ba57","tid":1807872,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT